com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.model

Interface IBMECMAuthenticator


  • public interface IBMECMAuthenticator
    Represents the protocol that must be implemented for a custom authentication mechanism to be used by this framework.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void authenticateWithUrl(String url, String username, String password, String desktopId, IBMECMCompletionHandler<CookieManager> onComplete)
      This method is called when the framework needs to establsh a session to IBM Content Navigator.

    • Method Detail

      • authenticateWithUrl

        void authenticateWithUrl(String url,
                         String username,
                         String password,
                         String desktopId,
                         IBMECMCompletionHandler<CookieManager> onComplete)
        This method is called when the framework needs to establsh a session to IBM Content Navigator. See IBMECMAuthenticatorDataSource for information about how the IBMECMAuthenticator instance is used.
        Parameters:
        url - the url that authentication is required for
        username - the user name to authenticate
        password - the user's password
        desktopId - the desktop id that the user wants to connect to
        onComplete - the completion closure that must be called when authentication is complete
